metadata.name: Artists Paintbrush
metadata.description:
In Search of Stillness: Journey Through the Pacific Northwest

Edition 1/1

Artist: Shaun Stewart

An incredible road trip through Oregon and Washington culminated with a final stop in Mt Rainier National Park. It was midsummer and the peak of wildflower season was coming to a close. After a spectacular day of hiking in the park, we arrived at Tipsoo Lake for sunset.

We watched the color set ablaze the hazy August sky from a splendid vista overlooking the lake and distant Rainier.
